•	25,000 HR policy documents, job descriptions, onboarding guides
•	25,000 legal and compliance documents
•	25,000 financial reports, quarterly summaries, budget documents
•	All synthetic — generated with Claude API using domain-specific templates

Evaluation Set
•	1,000 manually labeled query-document pairs (250 per domain)
•	Each pair has: query, relevant document(s), relevance label (0-3 graded), domain tag
•	Cross-domain eval set: 200 queries where training domain ≠ test domain

